<title>USA: PLC Systems names Dow president and CEO.</title>
<headline>PLC Systems names Dow president and CEO.</headline>
<dateline>FRANKLIN, Mass. 1997-08-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>The board of directors of PLC Systems Inc said Monday it had named William Dow, 51, as president and chief executive officer, effective immediately.</p>
<p>Previously, Dow was president and CEO of Deknatel Snowden Pencer Worldwide Inc, a medical device manufacturing and marketing subsidiary of Genzyme Corp.</p>
<p>At PLC, Dow replaces M. Lee Hibbs, who announced his resignation on April 22, effective July 31.</p>
